  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Venezuelan Refugee Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Entire families are forced to leave their homes with only what they can carry on their backs. The long journey across the Colombian border has become very common these days. The majority of Venezuelan refugees, who make it into Colombia, are sleeping in refugee camps, unemployed and without enough food. This fund will support Venezuelan refugees. We will work with other organizations in the Colombia-Venezuela border who are committed to providing assistance and support to those in need.</narrative>
  </description>
